<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>403</hymn_number>
<title>JESUH NIH A PEN ZUNGZAL CH403</title>
<key>E</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ni le thla a kal tawnnak lam, Jesuh a um a pen zungzal, A ngaite
 vawlei a deng tiang, A pennak a kau chinchin lai.

[V2]
 Holh phun dang hmangmi vialte nih, A dawtnak kha an thangthat cio,
 Ngakchia zong nih a vel-ngeihnak, Aw thlum tein hla kha an phuah.

[V3]
 A-mah sinah dong hin lo in, Thangthat le thlacam an kai ti; A min cu
 zi-hmui rimthaw bang, Zing fatein a kai zungzal.

[V4]
 Hi vawlei cung mi vialte nih, Kan Siangpahrang thangthat tuah u,
 Vancungmi hna tum than tuah u, Nan aw thlum in hla sa ve u.

[V5]
 Khua zakip kha Jesuh a uk, Thatnak a tam a karh chin ko; Sifakmi le
 re-theimi nih, A zungzal in an i lawm lai.</lyrics>
</song>